description: Putting the FUN in FUNdraising, Kona Ice of East Essex is giving back while giving out delicious shaved ice! Perfect for any occasion, Kona Ice is your #1 choice for fantastic treats everyone will love. With the softest ice around and the customizable power of their Flavor Wave station, that lets you flavor your ice just the way you like it, you're sure to love Kona Ice!
name: Kona Ice of East Essex
